{"tid":1650556,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"馬古尼：英格蘭後衛因為球會情況導致輸給捷克","createTime":"2019-10-13T04:33:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T04:34:39.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"10fdfd652c8615d243be6c2b183261a1b4e501e0","tid":1650556,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:33:45.000Z","msg":"英格蘭在歐洲國家盃外圍賽1：2輸給捷克，哈利馬古尼認為是球員在球會情況變差，禍延代表隊演出。<br />\n<br />\n英格蘭作客不敵捷克，令到外界批評聲音不絕。這條英軍防線有熱刺左閘丹尼路斯、愛華頓中堅米克堅尼及曼聯中堅馬古尼等，眾人的所屬球會今季表現都不好。<br />\n<br />\n馬古尼談及代表隊守將的情況時說：「我們把球會的狀態帶到國際賽舞台，令到比賽變得難踢。很明顯我們不在最佳狀態，所以受到懲罰。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGZqf9GMxMWJW6noFhHuW3mc%3D&h=cdfb332f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"61f26b0072e181c791fd59d68e7496b56f42a414","tid":1650556,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:34:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.thesun.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/ac-social-harry-maguire-shkodran-mustafi-1080.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F08%2Fac-social-harry-maguire-shkodran-mustafi-1080.jpg&h=21d4a0ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/metro.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/Untitled-collage-39-493c.jpg?quality=90&amp;strip=all&amp;zoom=1&amp;resize=644%2C364&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fmetro.co.uk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2FUntitled-collage-39-493c.jpg%3Fquality%3D90%26strip%3Dall%26zoom%3D1%26resize%3D644%252C364%26ssl%3D1&h=c297ee12&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}